  "text": "We randomly collected apps that use internet. For closedsource apps we mined the free apps on the Google Play store, and for the open-source apps we relied on the F-Droid software repository. [CITATION_1] For each app, we removed the duplicates, i.e., apps with the same package identifier, but different version numbers, and kept only the most recent version of the app. In the end, we collected 17 079 closed-source, and 432 opensource apps.",
